# VEHICLE::GET_VEHICLE_CLASS_FROM_NAME

## Summary
Returns the class of the specified vehicle

## Parameters
* **MODEL_NAMES** modelHashKey

## Returns
* **VEHICLE_CLASS**

## Useful links
- [VHub: Vehicles](https://vhub.wiki/vehicles)

## Notes
char buffer[128];
std::sprintf(buffer, "VEH_CLASS_%i", VEHICLE::GET_VEHICLE_CLASS_FROM_NAME (hash));

const char* className = HUD::GET_FILENAME_FOR_AUDIO_CONVERSATION(buffer);
